revisions.rev:
This is a '''list of albums''' attributed to the [[anime]] adaptation of ''[[Seto no Hanayome]]''. There have been five soundtrack singles released for the anime which contained the opening, ending, and insert songs featured in the anime series. There are six additional character song albums sung by the voice actors of six of the female characters.
(Note: All these are released under [[Avex Entertainment]], unless otherwise noted.)
